Danish pastries are actually Austrian (Viennese) in origin (in Danish, wienerbrød). But were still offered up by Denmark as their offering to the 2006 Café Europe dessert presentation: <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caf%C3%A9_Europe" target="_blank">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caf%C3%A9_Europe</a>

